Subject: Re: [T2] Heating possiblities

Tried one, they won't even clear the windshield very well below 50=B0 F.

About the only way you will get warm is to stuff it in your pocket...=20
(Don't do this either, you'll catch your clothes on fire).

Get the factory heater to 100% efficiency. I have a friend with a bus like=
=20
this. It will keep you warm if the weather is above freezing. Below that=20
you'll have to get creative.

Realistically the only electric heat that will do you any good is the 12=20
volt electric blankets or any of the electric heat clothing that us=20
motorcyclists use.

Many good things electric to wear in your bus in the motorcycle and=20
snowmobile catalogs. That way you heat you and not the air in your bus.



